aci\u00f3n de \u00c1reas Clave para la Biodiversidad, versi\u00f3n 1.2 229 Ap\u00e9ndice III: Estimaci\u00f3n del rango, extensi\u00f3n del h\u00e1bitat adecuado (ESH) y \u00e1rea de ocupaci\u00f3n (AOO) El Ap\u00e9ndice III.1 proporciona", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c57e0b32-0359-487f-8b92-377dd9b415a9": {"__data__": {"id_": "c57e0b32-0359-487f-8b92-377dd9b415a9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/directrices-para-el-uso-de-un-estandar-global-para-la-identificacion-de", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Directrices para el uso de un Est\u00e1ndar global para la identificaci\u00f3n de \u00c1reas Clave para la Biodiversidad : versi\u00f3n 1.2", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/directrices-para-el-uso-de-un-estandar-global-para-la-identificacion-de", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "4f4992458f1728d1e0087061ae4d0ba0efa1846f750e00450fc7978e559ade0e"}, "3": {"node_id": "33292af5-4faf-49b6-b693-07b68907f639", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/directrices-para-el-uso-de-un-estandar-global-para-la-identificacion-de", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "0110fb05de67db5ea6e39a5c2d8eb14d130a2db891393b7c899505970fdc7716"}}, "hash": "dde2aea6504baf84453cd33567ec1653be9458da4c8bc17e105e8bfea010ed51", "text"